    "On the firm side, we show that all results remain robust when controlling for firm characteristics (Table D.1), ensuring that observed differences across workplaces are not driven by variation in firm age, size, or productivity.",
    "On the worker side, we show that the results are similarly robust to controlling for workers' detailed task mixes within occupations, ensuring that the effects of employer encouragement are not merely driven by differences in task types more amenable to AI chatbot use.",
